[normal]A central element of the EU’s approach to tackling youth unemployment is the Youth Guarantee.
[normal] 
[normal]Could you summarise for us your understanding of the extent to which this has been taken up across the EU and whether there are signs that it is achieving any results yet?
[normal] 
[normal]If there are statistics available, perhaps you could identify the fact that they are and then
